Get Started

Platform software system

The platform is an innovative platform specifically for the AI ​​2.0 era. It provides efficient intelligent computing center management and operation tools for intelligent computing center managers, and provides a complete development tool chain for large model developers and application ISVs downwards. End-to-end AI applications are provided to end customers.

Platform service content

ecological services

Basic services based on computing power, data, models, and AI training incubate intelligent computing SAAS solutions to create a high-quality open innovation ecosystem and provide leading demonstrations and basic support for national and regional innovation capacity building.

model service

Provide large model model deployment inference and fine-tuning service capabilities, supporting evaluation and debugging auxiliary tools, accelerating the conversion of computing power into productivity

training services

Provides multiple types of services such as model development, training, deployment, and evaluation, as well as asset management capabilities such as images, data sets, and models.

Computing services

Based on the Alibaba Cloud Feitian platform, it provides a variety of basic cloud product services, including bare metal, container instances, ACK clusters, etc., to achieve stable and reliable computing services.

Storage service

Provide secure, stable, optimized and seamless cloud-based intelligent data storage services, providing multi-level storage, caching and data transmission capabilities.
